te-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.ufh.ac.za/timeline.html#\">Timeline of the University: 1959</a>  n<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20071230083858/http://www.ufh.ac.za/timeline.html%23\">Archived</a> December 30, 2007, at the <a href=\"/wiki/Wayback_Machine\" title=\"Wayback Machine\">Wayback Machine</a>.. Official website of University of Fort Hare. Accessed 2007-12-03.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-byrnes-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-byrnes_4-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-byrnes_4-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-byrnes_4-2\"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation book\">Byrnes, Rita M. (1996). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://countrystudies.us/south-africa/\"><i>South Africa: A Country Study</i></a>. Washington: GPO for the Library of Congress.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=South+Africa%3A+A+Country+Study&amp;rft.place=Washington&amp;rft.pub=GPO+for+the+Library+of+Congress&amp;rft.date=1996&amp;rft.aulast=Byrnes&amp;rft.aufirst=Rita+M.&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fcountrystudies.us%2Fsouth-africa%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABantu+Education+Act%2C+1953\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-giliomee-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-giliomee_5-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Giliomee H, 2009. <i>A Note on Bantu Education 1953-1970</i> South African Journal of Economics, March 2009.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://africanhistory.about.com/library/bl/blsaJune16decree.htm\">\"The Afrikaans Medium Decree that Led to the Soweto Uprising\"</a>. <i>about.com</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">15 September</span> 2017</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=about.com&amp;rft.atitle=The+Afrikaans+Medium+Decree+that+Led+to+the+Soweto+Uprising&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fafricanhistory.about.com%2Flibrary%2Fbl%2FblsaJune16decree.htm&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABantu+Education+Act%2C+1953\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\">(U.S.), Study Commission on U. S. Policy toward Southern Africa (15 September 1981). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://books.google.com/books?id=sq43lnbklEUC&amp;pg=PA119&amp;lpg=PA119&amp;dq=1979+south+african+education+and+training+act&amp;source=bl&amp;ots=arS1e7r4pN&amp;sig=QaEHHY_aOnRgIh7PgdlxkENlhGQ&amp;hl=en&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=0ahUKEwj-_bfyqc_UAhVL54MKHT8KAmUQ6AEIRzAF#v=onepage&amp;q=1979+south+african+education+and+training+act&amp;f=false\">\"South Africa: Time Running Out&#160;: the Report of the Study Commission on U.S. Policy Toward Southern Africa\"</a>. University of California Press<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">15 September</span> 2017</span>  &#8211; via Google Books.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=South+Africa%3A+Time+Running+Out+%3A+the+Report+of+the+Study+Commission+on+U.S.+Policy+Toward+Southern+Africa&amp;rft.pub=University+of+California+Press&amp;rft.date=1981-09-15&amp;rft.aulast=%28U.S.%29&amp;rft.aufirst=Study+Commission+on+U.+S.+Policy+toward+Southern+Africa&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3Dsq43lnbklEUC%26pg%3DPA119%26lpg%3DPA119%26dq%3D1979%2Bsouth%2Bafrican%2Beducation%2Band%2Btraining%2Bact%26source%3Dbl%26ots%3DarS1e7r4pN%26sig%3DQaEHHY_aOnRgIh7PgdlxkENlhGQ%26hl%3Den%26sa%3DX%26ved%3D0ahUKEwj-_bfyqc_UAhVL54MKHT8KAmUQ6AEIRzAF%23v%3Donepage%26q%3D1979%2Bsouth%2Bafrican%2Beducation%2Band%2Btraining%2Bact%26f%3Dfalse&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABantu+Education+Act%2C+1953\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"http://nmmu.ac.za/documents/mward/Bantu%20Education%20Act%201953.pdf\">http://nmmu.ac.za/documents/mward/Bantu%20Education%20Act%201953.pdf</a><sup class=\"noprint Inline-Template\"><span style=\"white-space: nowrap;\">&#91;<i><a href=\"/wiki/Wikipedia:Link_rot\" title=\"Wikipedia:Link rot\"><span title=\"&#160;Dead link since October 2016\">permanent dead link</span></a></i>&#93;</span></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_links\">External links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Bantu_Education_Act,_1953&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: External links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20051201041632/http://www.socsci.kun.nl/ped/whp/histeduc/apartheid.html\">Article on apartheid and education that mentions the Bantu Act</a> (in Dutch)</li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://nmmu.ac.za/documents/mward/Bantu%20Education%20Act%201953.pdf\">Text of the act</a><sup class=\"noprint Inline-Template\"><span style=\"white-space: nowrap;\">&#91;<i><a href=\"/wiki/Wikipedia:Link_rot\" title=\"W